# 📁 Project Structure

```
Generalised Data Structure Library.cpp
│
├── Singly Linked List
├── Doubly Linked List
├── Stack
├── Queue
└── Demo (main function)
```

---

# ▶️ Compilation

Using g++

```bash
g++ "Generalised Data Structure Library.cpp" -o DataStructureLibrary
```

Run

```bash
./DataStructureLibrary
```

On Windows (MinGW)

```bash
g++ "Generalised Data Structure Library.cpp" -o DataStructureLibrary.exe
DataStructureLibrary.exe
```

---

# 💻 Example Usage

```cpp
SinglyLLL<int> obj;

obj.InsertFirst(10);
obj.InsertFirst(20);
obj.InsertLast(30);

obj.Display();

cout << obj.Count();
```

Stack Example

```cpp
Stack<char> s;

s.push('A');
s.push('B');

cout << s.pop();
```

Queue Example

```cpp
Queue<double> q;

q.enqueue(10.5);
q.enqueue(20.7);

cout << q.dequeue();
```

---

# 📊 Time Complexity

## Singly Linked List

| Operation | Complexity |
|----------|------------|
| InsertFirst | O(1) |
| InsertLast | O(n) |
| DeleteFirst | O(1) |
| DeleteLast | O(n) |
| InsertAtPos | O(n) |
| DeleteAtPos | O(n) |
| Count | O(1) |

---

## Doubly Linked List

| Operation | Complexity |
|----------|------------|
| InsertFirst | O(1) |
| InsertLast | O(n) |
| DeleteFirst | O(1) |
| DeleteLast | O(n) |
| InsertAtPos | O(n) |
| DeleteAtPos | O(n) |
| Count | O(1) |

---

## Stack

| Operation | Complexity |
|----------|------------|
| Push | O(1) |
| Pop | O(1) |
| Peep | O(1) |
| Count | O(1) |

---

## Queue

| Operation | Complexity |
|----------|------------|
| Enqueue | O(1) |
| Dequeue | O(1) |
| Count | O(1) |

